    <item>
      <title>尽管销售缓慢，私募股权仍为股东带来意外之财</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/private-equity-hands-shareholders-windfall-despite-slow-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在交易长期停滞的情况下，私募股权公司正努力将现金重新交回基金投资者手中。他们与股东之间没有这个问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/private-equity-hands-shareholders-windfall-despite-slow-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 19:41:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
