      <title>凯雷合伙人携手房地产巨头 Hines 打造财富部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/carlyle-partner-joins-property-giant-hines-to-build-wealth-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国房地产巨头海因斯聘请了凯雷集团资深人士保罗·费拉罗 (Paul Ferraro) 为全球富人打造其部门，加入了越来越多专注于个人投资者的基金经理行列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/carlyle-partner-joins-property-giant-hines-to-build-wealth-unit</guid>
