    <item>
      <title>凯雷加入私募基金热潮，瞄准欧洲富人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/carlyle-joins-rush-of-private-credit-funds-tapping-europe-s-rich-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯雷集团 (Carlyle Group Inc.) 正与黑石集团 (Blackstone Inc.) 等巨头一道，竞相争夺欧洲大陆富裕投资者持有的数万亿美元资金，并正在为富裕个人准备其首个欧洲私人信贷基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/carlyle-joins-rush-of-private-credit-funds-tapping-europe-s-rich-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>回避股票和囤积现金正在损害欧洲财富</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-02-13/shunning-stocks-and-hoarding-cash-is-harming-european-wealth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资失败会让欧洲人变得更穷，并使国内公司缺乏股权资本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-02-13/shunning-stocks-and-hoarding-cash-is-harming-european-wealth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 05:00:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>收入超过杰米戴蒙的麦格理银行家辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/macquarie-s-highest-paid-banker-who-earned-more-than-dimon-steps-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦格理集团有限公司 (Macquarie Group Ltd.) 的大宗商品主管尼克·奥凯恩 (Nick O’Kane) 的收入比摩根大通 (JPMorgan Chase) 和摩根大通 (JPMorgan Chase) 等华尔街高管的收入还要高。公司的杰米戴蒙和花旗集团的简弗雷泽将于本月晚些时候辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/macquarie-s-highest-paid-banker-who-earned-more-than-dimon-steps-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 23:06:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
